    "• Dearth of market knowledge to make informed decision on cultivation of specific crops and use of appropriate technology for higher revenue.",
    "• Severe digital divide in rural areas hindering access to e-commerce platforms, online marketing, and financial services.",
    "• Lack of networking and marketing skills among small-scale farmers.",
    "• Creation of information platforms with real-time market prices and demand for facilitating decision-making.",
    "• Development of mobile applications in local language for facilitating access to local and cross-border buyers."
